<C>__{curtis}
<D>__{what are you reading?}
<A>__{danny tilts the book to show him: history of political philosophy.}
<C>__{curtis}
<D>__{leo strauss...}
<P>__{(nods approvingly)}
<D>__{i've got to go to boston. i came to say goodbye.}
<C>__{danny}
